title: Vestal puts up another zero, 5-0 over Horseheads
text:
Vestal puts up another zero, 5-0 over Horseheads 
By wbng sports October 12, 2015 Updated Oct 12, 2015 at 11:47 PM EDT 
Vestal, NY (WBNG Binghamton) Fourteen games into the season and the Vestal girls soccer team has still not allowed an opposing goal. The Golden Bears beat Horseheads, 5-0, Monday to improve to 14-0. 
Victoria McKnight and Olivia McKnight each scored a goal late in the first half for Vestal. Madeline Beaulieu netted a pair in the second half.
